      const scaledUrl = await downscaleDataUrl(src, 4096);
      const prompt = `You are an expert at analyzing architectural and engineering drawings with perfect vision.

Scan the ENTIRE drawing systematically (top-left to bottom-right, room by room, section by section).

Detect and count EVERY type of object you can identify. Common symbols in fire/HVAC/electrical drawings:
- Detectors (smoke, heat, fire, motion)
- Doors (arcs + door lines)
- Windows (parallel lines in walls)
- Sprinklers, pulls, alarms, horns, strobes
- Electrical outlets, switches, panels
- Ducts, vents, diffusers
- Rooms (enclosed areas)
- Equipment symbols

Return ONLY a JSON object (no markdown, no explanation) in this exact format:
{
  "total": <total count of all detected objects>,
  "byType": [
    { "type": "<object type name in Hebrew or English as user expects>", "count": <number>, "icon": "<single emoji>" }
  ],
  "summary": "<one-line description of what was found>"
}

Example: {"total": 24, "byType": [{"type":"גלאים","count":12,"icon":"🔴"},{"type":"דלתות","count":8,"icon":"🚪"},{"type":"חדרים","count":4,"icon":"🏠"}], "summary":"..."}

Be precise — scan every part of the drawing carefully. Do not miss anything.`;

      const resp = await fetch(CHAT_RESPOND_ENDPOINT, {
        method: 'POST',
