- If the user asks a QUESTION about the image (e.g. "how many rooms?", "כמה מנורות?", "what do you see?") rather than an editing instruction, return an empty operations array and put your answer in the "summary" field. Example: {"operations":[],"summary":"I can see 5 light fixtures in the drawing."}

Reply with ONLY the JSON object.`;

